            <who name="Knut Anders Hatlen">knut.hatlen</who>
            <bug_when>2009-10-31 16:42:40 +0000</bug_when>
            <thetext>Fixed in changeset 893:fba450bedb13. File list is now hidden by default, but can be made visible by clicking &quot;show modified files&quot;.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
